{
  "1801140": {
    "name": "Guns Undarkness",
    "steam_appid": 1801140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款由参与了《女神异闻录》系列和《真·女神转生》系列的目黑将司掌舵开发的策略JRPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制独一无二的武器，在严酷的战场上驰骋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加强与同伴之间的联系，提高合作能力，在与敌人的战斗中取得优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・受《METAL GEAR SOLID》和《女神异闻录》启发的回合制指令战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・通过加深与同伴的情谊来增强主角能力的交流系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・游戏背景是濒临毁灭的未来世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・由目黑将司（《女神异闻录》《真·女神转生》）、lya Kuvshinov（《攻壳机动队：SAC_2045》《生日幻境》）和Lotus Juice（《女神异闻录》系列）共同呈献。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/f1939d2b453ce99887dbc99fb6e75b84.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2045年，受益于现代科技的强大发展，人类迎来了短暂的平静。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但与此同时，富人与穷人之间的社会差距也成为了一个严重的问题， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在“穷人”中，出现了一群打着“原始主义”旗号策划着“大重启”的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们的名字叫“千之高原”。以他们手中的两枚核导弹为导火索，全球爆发了大规模核战争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至此，“大重启”完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公作为一家私人军事公司的成员，将与同伴们一起克服这一困难局面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而在这个满目疮痍的世界里，能否发现“真实的爱”， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并彻底改变人类，取决于你的行动。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/cd3e19674693a05ed8480512603689aa.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战场上，玩家将操控主角，与伙伴（最多三人）一起征战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（游戏采用明雷遇敌系统） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/e8cc88d7950234ec47dba7015c62a7c3.webp?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用“手势”按钮指定要让同伴躲藏的掩体，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按下“GO”按钮，让同伴执行躲藏动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果发现了敌人，请就位并射击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/fdbf96da6ed1e5696d677945da7cde15.poster.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/fdbf96da6ed1e5696d677945da7cde15.webm?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/fdbf96da6ed1e5696d677945da7cde15.mp4?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果主人公和所有同伴都处于躲藏状态（在掩体后），此时射击敌人，可以发动总攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在规定时间内连按按钮的次数越多，敌人在战斗阶段的生命值就越少。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦击中敌人，就会进入战斗阶段， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗系统是指令选择式的回合制战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/61ceb25ad9e924e49403c67a8c564c42.poster.avif?t=1766054368\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/61ceb25ad9e924e49403c67a8c564c42.webm?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/61ceb25ad9e924e49403c67a8c564c42.mp4?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“普通攻击（ATTACK）”是不消耗 SP（技能点数）的基础攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“技能（SKILL）”可进行更加强力的攻击，但需要消耗SP。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在“躲藏状态”下，无需消耗SP就可以使用技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(使用技能后，将结束躲藏状态）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击者的枪械类别（手枪、步枪、霰弹枪、狙击步枪、微型冲锋枪）与被攻击者的防具之间存在相性， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相性决定了各单位的WEAK（弱点）和RESIST（防御），对WEAK造成的伤害更高，对RESIST造成的伤害更少。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果同伴的攻击成功击中了敌人的弱点，该角色就会进入躲藏状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能种类繁多，有威力强大的技能、能瞬间致死的技能、增益技能和减益技能， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据枪械的不同，技能也有很多变化。　　 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗胜利后，将会获得经验值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当经验值积累到一定数量时，等级将会提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/8fa409b6e8e495b9d0aae33257799ea4.webp?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/de2389fc4c0baa17b4c40f8c4f4e5ff5.poster.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/de2389fc4c0baa17b4c40f8c4f4e5ff5.webm?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/de2389fc4c0baa17b4c40f8c4f4e5ff5.mp4?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经验值分为“角色经验”和“枪械经验”两种， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种经验值积累到一定数量时都会提升等级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色经验可提高角色的参数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >枪械经验会增加可使用的技能数量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/3f62aa39fd8a43a34a3b16141084ff24.webp?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/471652166595811c821a21982815118e.poster.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/471652166595811c821a21982815118e.webm?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/471652166595811c821a21982815118e.mp4?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平日的阿尔法小队都聚集在突击登陆潜艇—— “玛伦号”上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以从任务面板上接受任务，也可以从大地图上指定一个登陆点，前往商店等不同地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/bee42cff7e0208939d88e6f11ed81f23.webp?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/0d4778500d9b41f4ee14c153a9fd014c.poster.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/0d4778500d9b41f4ee14c153a9fd014c.webm?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/0d4778500d9b41f4ee14c153a9fd014c.mp4?t=1766054368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >持有的枪械可以通过各种部件来进行强化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，随着剧情的发展还可以获得枪支蓝图， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以用收集到的材料来制造新的枪械。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/c250ee59044f40fcb3b4cbce2c9567fa.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿尔法小队是美国私人军事公司BTI麾下的小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BTI内设多个分队，“阿尔法小队”是以BTI招募的前海军陆战队员麦戈文少校为中心而组建的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最初的四名成员包括麦戈文、她在海军陆战队期间的部下威尔和扎克，以及高性能战斗机器人直美。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >后来，又有一名新兵（玩家本人）加入，阿尔法小队成为一支五人小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/a5b51bbd55880ec81759bf492edda940.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事的主角，也是你自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在私人军事公司一路打拼，跳槽到BTI阿尔法小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小队看中你非凡的战斗能力，小队成员中唯独给你配备了最新TAGS装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/468dc8cef9b564c4227afd2726f4b382.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开朗、积极的17岁女孩。 是伟大科学家科恩博士的独生女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然她与科恩博士的关系并不好，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但核战争爆发后，她接手了父亲的研究工作，并努力为人类开辟更光明的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/396413fb216d0c61e76cf331d3e0cbb0.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公的好兄弟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然也有太过认真不通人性的地方， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在战斗中，他作为霰弹枪专家为阿尔法小队提供支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他和阿尔法小队指挥官麦戈文是前上下级关系，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾与扎克一起在美国海军陆战队服役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/aa5a79f3f98812a12208bd4e6299be6e.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高性能战斗机器人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有情感，能与人类无差异地交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有像母亲一样温柔的性格， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿尔法小队可靠的进攻手，凭借一把手枪就可在战场上纵横驰骋。      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/53202b956c4ff3e37978f2d0b1dbd095.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉默寡言的神秘雇佣兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年轻时，曾作为杀手暗中活动，后来被千之高原的首领张元帅纳入麾下，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从此一直承担着千之高原的见不得光的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊技能是“高速移动”，能以超越TAGS极限的反应速度躲避子弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/3c51116d865f2c50fb7cfc5da651d4f6.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引发了核战争的军事政权国家，位于远东地区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以丈元帅为领导者，该国奉行“原始主义”思想，认为人类应该放弃科技，回到“原始时代”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将整个世界引向了毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核战争后，开始散布“原始主义”思想，通过无止境的掠夺使世界陷入混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/0b73e122c4fba305ee96221f69b051d4.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/3640d126d8b6fbe8f3ed6db929856714.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【崩溃的近未来城市】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核战争结束后，一些城市还保留着少量科技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个时代相对富裕的人们在此定居，但此地也因此成为原始主义者的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/bcddf849d799a92cb7f52479e96ba203.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【西海岸村】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核战争后，穷人们聚集到这个村子，对抗原始主义者掠夺的组织也是在这里成立的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/a1b8de9685fff41fdac2d3f500fe2902.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=245 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【研究设施】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核战争前曾有大型研究城市的地区的设施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战后这些设施已被废弃，但仍保留着重要的研究材料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801140/extras/3ade7b822eb24ae446c8208d146ae010.avif?t=1766054368\" width=680 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・游戏设计、音乐、开发：目黑将司（《女神异闻录》系列、《真·女神转生》系列）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・角色设计：Ilya Kuvshinov（《攻壳机动队：SAC_2045》、《生日幻境》）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・作词：Lotus Juice（《女神异闻录》系列）</p>",
